                        "text": "The banshee unleashes a soul-chilling <i>wail of the banshee</i> (DC 38). This Wail overcomes <i>silence</i> and similar effects of 5th level or lower. The banshee can instead use Wail as a three-action activity to overcome such effects of up to 8th level.<br/> The banshee\u2019s Wail resonates for 1 round, and any creature that comes within the area during that time must attempt a save against the effect. A creature can\u2019t be affected more than once by the same Wail. The banshee can\u2019t Wail again for 1d4 rounds."
